page_title: 'Use your image data with Azure OpenAI Service in Azure OpenAI Studio'
page_description: Use this article to learn about using your image data for image generation in Azure OpenAI.
chunk_content: Prerequisites- An Azure subscription - Create one for free.- An Azure OpenAI resource with the GPT-4 Turbo with Vision model deployed. For more information about model deployment, see the resource deployment guide.* At least the Cognitive Services Contributor role assigned to you for the Azure OpenAI resource.
